  "title": "FROM $1000/mth + COMMS | Student Adviser",
  "description": "<p><strong>Unlock Your Earning Potential While You Study! [SG/PR ONLY]</strong></p>\n<p> If you’re looking for a hands-on, client-focused career with <strong>high earning potential</strong>, this is your chance to explore financial advisory while still in school!</p>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p>\n<p>✔ Break Out of the Rat Race – Your effort = your earnings. No fixed salary cap, no waiting for promotions</p>\n<p>✔ <strong>Learn Beyond the Textbooks</strong> – Get hands-on experience in personal finance, investments &amp; wealth planning</p>\n<p>✔ <strong>Flexibility</strong> – Work around your schedule, perfect for students</p>\n<p>✔ <strong>Fast-Tracked Growth</strong> – Gain direct mentorship, ChFC certifications &amp; industry knowledge while others are still figuring out their path</p>\n<p>✔ <strong>Commission &amp; Incentives-Based</strong> – Earn what you’re worth-put in the work, reap the rewards</p>\n<p><strong>As per FAA-N13, only individuals with the following will be considered:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Minimum DOB 2004</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Minimum Local Polytechnic Diploma</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Who Should Apply?</strong></p>\n<p>✅ Students eager to gain <strong>real-world financial exposure</strong></p>\n<p>✅ Go-getters who want to <strong>earn beyond a fixed pay check</strong></p>\n<p>✅ Those who want a <strong>head start in the finance industry</strong></p>\n<p>✅ Anyone looking to develop <strong>valuable sales &amp; communication skills</strong></p>\n<p>No prior experience? No problem. We provide the <strong>training, mentorship &amp; support;</strong>you bring the drive.</p>\n<p><strong>Apply now &amp; start building your financial future today!</strong></p>\n<p>Job Type: Part-time</p>\n<p>Pay: $500.00 - $2,000.00 per month</p>",
